T*
(errors are divided into two categories: expected and unexpected . Expected errors Expected) Tj
T*
(errors happen during normal operation. Examples: Validation errors when the user enters invalid) Tj
T*
(data. You can?t control what the user types! Network errors when the user?s network fails. It?s) Tj
